<br>
We use a normal DKP (call it cp fo counterpoints) without any adjustments. Just plain get points for attending a raid and spend points on loot. Officers and members all have the same rights to loot all classes too (well we dont give FT or focus items to warriors or haste or vengeance to clerics, but thats about it)<br>
<br>
The one i heard about has the same but also timepoints and other points i cant recall, hehe.<br>
