<br>
In all cases the item still costs points.  On rare occasions when nobody wants it the officers will permanently reduce the point value on the item.  If we notice a lot of stuff rotting we know it's time to move on.  /em waves sadly at Ntov <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=472195">Khumak</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
